Name: FString
Unique name for the target.
ConflictStatus: Whether the target has outstanding conflicts that require resolution.
TargetDependencies: Text present in these targets will not be duplicated in this target.
AdditionalManifestDependencies: Text present in these manifests will not be duplicated in this target.
RequiredModuleNames: The names of modules which must be loaded when gathering text. Use to gather from packages or metadata sourced from a module that isn't the primary game module.
GatherFromTextFiles: Parameters for defining what text is gathered from text files and how.
GatherFromPackages: Parameters for defining what text is gathered from packages and how.
GatherFromMetaData: Parameters for defining what text is gathered from metadata and how.
ImportDialogueSettings: Settings for importing dialogue from WAV files.
NativeCultureIndex: The index of the native culture among the supported cultures.
SupportedCulturesStatistics: Cultures for which the source text is being localized for.
